<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Challenge Not Approved</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #fff5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .observation {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .observation-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #495057;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 10px 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .actions {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">PropFirm Platform</div>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="title">Challenge Not Approved</h1>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear Trader,</p>
            
            <p>We regret to inform you that your <strong>{{challengeType}}</strong> challenge has not been approved at this time.</p>
            
            <div class="highlight">
                <p><strong>Challenge Status:</strong> Not Approved</p>
                <p><strong>Challenge Type:</strong> {{challengeType}}</p>
                <p><strong>Account Size:</strong> ${{accountSize}}</p>
                <p><strong>Review Date:</strong> {{reviewDate}}</p>
            </div>
            
            {{#if observation}}
            <div class="observation">
                <div class="observation-title">Review Comments:</div>
                <p>{{observation}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <p>Don't let this discourage you! This is part of the learning process, and we encourage you to:</p>
            
            <ul>
                <li>Review your trading strategy and risk management</li>
                <li>Analyze your trading performance during the challenge</li>
                <li>Consider starting a new challenge when you're ready</li>
                <li>Reach out to our support team if you have any questions</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>Remember, successful trading requires patience, discipline, and continuous improvement. We believe in your potential and look forward to seeing your progress in future challenges.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="actions">
            <a href="{{landingUrl}}/challenges" class="button">Start New Challenge</a>
            <a href="{{landingUrl}}/support" class="button">Contact Support</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The PropFirm Team</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            <p><small>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>